dct_description_sm: Shows: principal buildings, railways, water locks, warehouses, quays. "Confidential." Includes inset map: Gironde estuary ports (scale 1:2,500,000). At foot of legend: "1943 base map, corrected by aerial photographs." At bottom left: "No. 3122. 28 February 1944." Oriented with north to the left. Index to numbered quays on verso.
dct_creator_sm: United States. Office of Strategic Services. Research and Analysis Branch
dct_publisher_sm: [Washington, D.C.] : Office of Strategic Services. Research and Analysis Branch, 1944.
